# This file is parsed through the hwrf.conf [holdvars] configuration
# section.  It is used to control the workflow for the NCO J-Jobs, and
# can also be used for debugging: simply source the
# storm*.holdvars.txt in a ksh/sh/bash shell, set PYTHONPATH and then
